"^(bundle://|https?://|data:|assets/|client://)"},{"$ref":"#/$defs/Binding"}],"description":"Reference to an asset (image, font, audio, video, SVG, …). Five\nscheme prefixes are accepted, picked by the runtime to dispatch\nthe right loader:\n\n- `bundle://<path>` — asset packaged inside the active bundle.\n- `https://<url>` / `http://<url>` — fetched over the network and\n  cached on first render.\n- `data:<mime>;base64,<payload>` (or `data:<mime>,<urlencoded>`) —\n  inline bytes carried in the DSL itself.\n- `assets/<path>` — Flutter-style local asset path declared in the\n  consumer app's pubspec asset list (used by host integrations that\n  ship icon SVGs alongside the runtime).\n- `client://<channel>/<id>` — resource served by the client / host\n  process via an MCP client-extension channel.\n\nUsed cross-schema by `app` (splash · publisher logos · font\nassets), `page`/widgets (image · icon · BackgroundImage · video\nsrc), and `theme` (font asset registration). Lives under\n`configs/_primitive/` for that reason."},"BackgroundImage":{"type":"object","properties":{"image":{"$ref":"#/$defs/AssetRef"},"fit":{"enum":["fill","contain","cover","fitWidth","fitHeight","none","scaleDown"],"default":"cover"},"alignment":{"$ref":"#/$defs/Alignment"},"opacity":{"type":"number","minimum":0,"maximum":1},"colorFilter":{"type":"object","properties":{"color":{"type":"string"},"blendMode":{"enum":["srcIn","color","screen","overlay","multiply"],"default":"srcIn","description":"Curated subset of blend modes covering the common tinting use cases (`srcIn` for solid tint, `color` for hue swap, `screen`/`overlay`/`multiply` for atmosphere)."}},"required":["color"],"additionalProperties":false},"repeat":{"enum":["noRepeat","repeat","repeatX","repeatY"],"default":"noRepeat"}},"required":["image"],"additionalProperties":false,"description":"Image fill behind a box's content. `image` accepts the same forms as\nthe `image` widget's `src` (`bundle://`, `https?://`, `data:`,\n`client://`). `fit` and `alignment` mirror the `image` widget's\nsemantics. `opacity` applies an alpha multiplier; `colorFilter`\ncomposites a tint via the named blend mode. `repeat` controls\ntiling behaviour outside the image's natural bounds."},"Binding":{"type":"string","pattern":"^\\{\\{.*\\}\\}$","description":"Binding-expression string of the form `\"{{...}}\"`. Authors may\nsubstitute any primitive value with a binding so the runtime\nresolves the value at render time. Used as an alternative branch\nin primitives that otherwise expect a specific structural shape\n(AssetRef, Dimension, BorderRadius, Alignment, …)."},"BorderRadius":{"oneOf":[{"type":"number","minimum":0},{"type":"object","properties":{"topStart":{"type":"number","minimum":0},"topEnd":{"type":"number","minimum":0},"bottomStart":{"type":"number","minimum":0},"bottomEnd":{"type":"number","minimum":0},"all":{"type":"number","minimum":0}},"additionalProperties":false},{"$ref":"#/$defs/Binding"}],"description":"Per-corner radius value. A bare number applies uniformly to all\nfour corners; the object form lets each corner take an independent\nradius. `all` is a shorthand for setting every corner at once and\nis overridden by individual corner keys.\n\nCorner names are **directional** (RTL-aware) per Material 3:\n\n- `topStart` — top corner on the leading edge (top-left in LTR,\n  top-right in RTL).\n- `topEnd` — top corner on the trailing edge.\n- `bottomStart` / `bottomEnd` — same convention on the bottom row.\n\nThis is the cross-schema canonical for any \"per-corner radius\"\nshape — referenced by `theme.Shape` (M3 shape token sizes) and by\nthe `BoxDecoration.borderRadius` widget property."},"ChannelDefinition":{"type":"object","properties":{"type":{"type":"string","description":"Channel type — `client.watchFile`, `client.watchDirectory`, `client.systemMonitor`, `client.poll`, `client.websocket` per §8.6.2."},"url":{"type":"string"},"tool":{"type":"string"},"params":{"type":"object","additionalProperties":true},"binding":{"type":"string"},"lifecycle":{"$ref":"#/$defs/ChannelLifecycle"},"onMessage":{"$ref":"#/$defs/ActionOrList"},"onConnect":{"$ref":"#/$defs/ActionOrList"},"onDisconnect":{"$ref":"#/$defs/ActionOrList"},"onError":{"$ref":"#/$defs/ActionOrList"}},"required":["type"],"additionalProperties":true,"description":"Long-lived bidirectional stream per docs/08_Client_Extensions.md §8.6."},"ChannelLifecycle":{"type":"object","properties":{"autoStart":{"type":"boolean","default":false},"autoDispose":{"type":"boolean","default":false},"restartOnError":{"type":"boolean","default":false},"maxRestarts":{"type":"integer","minimum":0,"default":3},"restartDelay":{"type":"integer","minimum":0,"default":1000},"restartBackoff":{"enum":["fixed","linear","exponential"],"default":"fixed"}},"additionalProperties":false,"description":"Channel lifecycle config per docs/08_Client_Extensions.md §8.6.5."},"ChannelMap":{"type":"object","additionalProperties":{"$ref":"#/$defs/ChannelDefinition"}},"Dimension":{"oneOf":[{"type":"number"},{"type":"object","properties":{"value":{"type":"number"},"unit":{"type":"string"}},"required":["value"],"additionalProperties":false},{"$ref":"#/$defs/Binding"}],"description":"Numeric size — accepts a plain `number` (logical pixels) OR the\nlegacy MCP UI DSL v1.0 `{value, unit}` object form. The `unit`\nfield is informational; the runtime treats every dimension as\nlogical pixels."},"Gradient":{"type":"object","properties":{"type":{"enum":["linear","radial","sweep"]},"colors":{"type":"array","items":{"type":"string"},"minItems":2},"stops":{"type":"array","items":{"type":"number","minimum":0,"maximum":1}},"begin":{"$ref":"#/$defs/Alignment"},"end":{"$ref":"#/$defs/Alignment"},"center":{"$ref":"#/$defs/Alignment"},"radius":{"type":"number","minimum":0},"startAngle":{"type":"number"},"endAngle":{"type":"number"},"tileMode":{"enum":["clamp","repeated","mirror"],"default":"clamp"}},"required":["type","colors"],"additionalProperties":false,"description":"Multi-stop gradient fill. Selected by `type`:\n\n- `linear` — straight axis from `begin` (default `centerLeft`) to\n  `end` (default `centerRight`).\n- `radial` — circular gradient out from `center` (default `center`)\n  to `radius` (default `0.5`, expressed as a fraction of the\n  bounding rectangle's longest side).\n- `sweep` — angular gradient around `center`, swept from\n  `startAngle` (default `0`) to `endAngle` (default `2π`) in\n  radians.\n\n`colors` lists at least two color values; `stops` (optional) places\neach color at a position in `[0, 1]`. `tileMode` controls behaviour\npast the gradient extents."},"LifecycleHooks":{"type":"object","properties":{"onInit":{"$ref":"#/$defs/ActionOrList"},"onReady":{"$ref":"#/$defs/ActionOrList"},"onMount":{"$ref":"#/$defs/ActionOrList"},"onPause":{"$ref":"#/$defs/ActionOrList"},"onResume":{"$ref":"#/$defs/ActionOrList"},"onUnmount":{"$ref":"#/$defs/ActionOrList"},"onDestroy":{"$ref":"#/$defs/ActionOrList"}},"additionalProperties":false},"NavigationStyle":{"type":"object","properties":{"backgroundColor":{"type":"string"},"backgroundImage":{"$ref":"#/$defs/BackgroundImage"},"indicatorColor":{"type":"string","description":"Selection indicator pill color (rail / drawer / tabs)."},"indicatorShape":{"$ref":"#/$defs/BorderRadius","description":"Selection indicator corner radius. Defaults to a fully-rounded pill."},"dividerColor":{"type":"string","description":"Drawer-only — color of dividers between item groups."},"dividerThickness":{"$ref":"#/$defs/Dimension"},"dividerIndent":{"$ref":"#/$defs/Dimension","description":"Drawer-only — leading inset before each divider."},"labelStyle":{"$ref":"#/$defs/TextStyle","description":"Default text style for item labels (selected and unselected). Per-item override via NavItem.style.labelStyle."},"iconStyle":{"type":"object","properties":{"color":{"type":"string"},"size":{"$ref":"#/$defs/Dimension"}},"additionalProperties":false,"description":"Default icon color and size."},"selectedColor":{"type":"string","description":"Foreground color (icon + label) for the selected item."},"unselectedColor":{"type":"string","description":"Foreground color for non-selected items."},"elevation":{"$ref":"#/$defs/Dimension"}},"additionalProperties":false,"description":"Visual styling for a navigation surface (drawer / rail / tabs /\nbottomBar). Every field is optional — omitted fields fall back to\nthe active theme's component defaults. Used by\n`NavigationConfig.style` (whole surface) and `NavItem.style`\n(per-item override).\n\nBackgrounds compose: `backgroundColor` paints first, then\n`backgroundImage` paints over it."},"PermissionDeclaration":{"oneOf":[{"type":"array","items":{"type":"string"}},{"enum":["readonly","interactive","full"]},{"type":"object","additionalProperties":{"oneOf":[{"type":"array","items":{"type":"string"}},{"type":"object","additionalProperties":true}]}}],"description":"Permissions per docs/08_Client_Extensions.md §8.4. Either a list of permission names, a profile shorthand, or an object grouped by category."},"RouteTransition":{"type":"object","properties":{"style":{"enum":["slide","fade","scale","cube","sharedAxis","fadeThrough"]},"duration":{"$ref":"#/$defs/Dimension","description":"Total transition duration in milliseconds. Defaults to the M3 motion-system value for the chosen style."},"curve":{"$ref":"#/$defs/AnimationCurve","description":"Easing curve for the transition's progress. Defaults to `emphasized`."},"axis":{"enum":["horizontal","vertical"],"description":"Direction for `slide` / `sharedAxis`. Defaults to `horizontal`."},"reverse":{"type":"boolean","default":false,"description":"When true, run the transition in reverse direction (for back navigation)."}},"required":["style"],"additionalProperties":false,"description":"Per-route page transition. Declared on a `RouteValue` so every\n`navigate` to that route uses the same transition, OR overridden\ninline on a `navigate` action. Six canonical styles:\n\n- `slide` — incoming page slides over the outgoing along the\n  direction (M3 default for forward navigation).\n- `fade` — cross-fade between pages at the same position.\n- `scale` — outgoing scales out, incoming scales in.\n- `cube` — perspective-rotate as if turning a 3D cube; needs a\n  perspective-aware compositor (falls back to `slide` when\n  unavailable).\n- `sharedAxis` — coordinated slide+fade across an axis (M3 motion\n  pattern for sibling-level navigation).\n- `fadeThrough` — outgoing fades out while incoming fades in\n  after a brief zero-opacity bridge (M3 motion pattern for\n  top-level navigation)."},"SemverLike":{"type":"string","pattern":"^[0-9]+(\\.[0-9]+){0,2}(-[0-9A-Za-z.-]+)?$"},"StateBlock":{"type":"object","properties":{"initial":{"type":"object","additionalProperties":true}},"additionalProperties":false},"TextStyle":{"oneOf":[{"type":"string","pattern":"^\\{\\{.*\\}\\}$","description":"Binding expression that resolves to a TextStyle object — typically `{{theme.typography.<role>}}`."},{"type":"object","properties":{"fontFamily":{"oneOf":[{"type":"string"},{"type":"array","items":{"type":"string"}}]},"fontSize":{"$ref":"#/$defs/Dimension"},"fontWeight":{"oneOf":[{"type":"number"},{"enum":["thin","extraLight","light","normal","medium","semiBold","bold","extraBold","black","regular","w100","w200","w300","w400","w500","w600","w700","w800","w900"]},{"$ref":"#/$defs/Binding"}]},"fontStyle":{"oneOf":[{"enum":["normal","italic"]},{"$ref":"#/$defs/Binding"}]},"color":{"type":"string"},"backgroundColor":{"type":"string"},"letterSpacing":{"$ref":"#/$defs/Dimension"},"wordSpacing":{"$ref":"#/$defs/Dimension"},"height":{"$ref":"#/$defs/Dimension","description":"Line-height multiplier — `height * fontSize` is the per-line vertical advance."},"decoration":{"oneOf":[{"enum":["none","underline","overline","lineThrough"]},{"$ref":"#/$defs/Binding"}]},"decorationColor":{"type":"string"},"decorationStyle":{"oneOf":[{"enum":["solid","double","dotted","dashed","wavy"]},{"$ref":"#/$defs/Binding"}]},"decorationThickness":{"$ref":"#/$defs/Dimension"},"fontFeatures":{"type":"array","items":{"type":"string"},"description":"OpenType feature tags (`smcp`, `lnum`, `tnum`, `liga`, `dlig`, …)."},"shadows":{"type":"array","items":{"type":"object","properties":{"color":{"type":"string"},"offset":{"type":"object","properties":{"dx":{"type":"number"},"dy":{"type":"number"},"x":{"type":"number"},"y":{"type":"number"}},"additionalProperties":false,"description":"`{dx, dy}` (canonical) or `{x, y}` (legacy alias) offset."},"blurRadius":{"$ref":"#/$defs/Dimension"}},"required":["color"],"additionalProperties":false}},"shader":{"$ref":"#/$defs/Gradient","description":"Gradient/shader fill applied to the rendered text via a shader mask. When set, `color` is ignored."}},"additionalProperties":false}],"description":"Inline text style applied per `text` widget instance. Layered on\ntop of an M3 typography role when `variant` is set, or used\nstandalone. Mirrors the theme `TextStyle` token shape (fontFamily,\nfontSize, fontWeight, lineHeight, letterSpacing, fontFeatureSettings)\nand adds the per-instance fields a content app needs: color,\ndecoration, shader (gradient fill), and shadow stack."},"ValidationConfig":{"oneOf":[{"type":"object","additionalProperties":{"oneOf":[{"$ref":"#/$defs/ValidationRule"},{"type":"array","items":{"$ref":"#/$defs/ValidationRule"}}]}},{"type":"array","items":{"$ref":"#/$defs/ValidationRule"}}],"description":"Form validation per page. Shape A (object keyed by field) or Shape B (rule list)."},"ValidationRule":{"type":"object","properties":{"field":{"type":"string"},"type":{"type":"string"},"value":{},"message":{"type":"string"},"trigger":{"enum":["change","blur","submit"]}},"additionalProperties":true},"Widget":{"type":"object","properties":{"type":{"type":"string"}},"required":["type"],"additionalProperties":true,"description":"Widget per docs/02_Widgets.md. Validated against the union in widgets.schema.json; left permissive here."}}}''';

